{"tid":1073324,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"港女：為何我們都喜歡條件好的人？","createTime":"2019-03-22T14:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T15:50:12.000Z","uid":27415,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"97c3a3d21f70e690e05dc13a1a730812a9cce920","tid":1073324,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:56:38.000Z","msg":"為什麼我們喜歡「條件好」的人？<br />\n<br />\n有一位同學名叫「血清素」，它有很多作用，比如說讓人更有耐心，讓人心情愉悅，血清素降低的時候會得抑鬱症。<br />\n<br />\n但是它在擇偶中有個很奇怪的表現。<br />\n<br />\n當你看到「條件好」，通常是指社會地位較高，較富有或者在某一方面特別突出的人，血清素就會大量分泌，讓你對這個人產生「好感」，想和他交往。<br />\n<br />\n如果說不看條件的就是「真愛」，那其實就是這人讓你產生了多巴胺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n如果說是「愛的是他的身份地位」，更多是這人讓你產生了血清素。<br />\n<br />\n不用不好意思承認自己喜歡「成功人士」，我們的身體就是這麼勢利。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"04ac46487a60c1d3ab4295bc670828193866c8fe","tid":1073324,"uid":27415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到有個長期single既舊同學post呢篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46376807469e84a3333b1607e378b5e76e9e4367","tid":1073324,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"04ac46487a60c1d3ab4295bc670828193866c8fe","tid":1073324,"uid":27415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到有個長期single既舊同學post呢篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:58:02.000Z","msg":"That&rsquo;s why it always single"},{"pid":"600f74b7256bb162b768df02f05426b87d0220f2","tid":1073324,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"46376807469e84a3333b1607e378b5e76e9e4367","tid":1073324,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"04ac46487a60c1d3ab4295bc670828193866c8fe","tid":1073324,"uid":27415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到有個長期single既舊同學post呢篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime